# Native audio (`audio-engine`)

Real-time path: C++17 Oboe + optional UAC2/libusb isoch. Kotlin JNI facades in `org.openmultitrack.audio`.

## Callback thread rules (non-negotiable)

On Oboe / UAC2 callback threads:

- ✅ Copy samples in/out of **SPSC** ring buffers (`spsc_ring_buffer.h`)
- ✅ Fixed-stack meter taps
- ❌ No `malloc` / `new`, locks, mutexes, file I/O, logging floods
- ❌ No JNI upcalls that allocate

Disk writers and readers run on **separate** Kotlin/native threads.

## Dual backend

`usb-audio` `AudioEngineRouter` picks `OBOE` vs `UAC2`. Do not bypass the router from `app`.

## Testing

- Descriptor/unit: `./scripts/run-uac2-native-tests.sh`
- Device: `audio-engine/src/androidTest/`, hardware scripts under `scripts/`

